contentTypes.name: Landing Page
contentTypes.description: Represents a Landing Page and its metadata. Contains a list of Landing Page Sections

contentTypes.name: Landing Page Section
contentTypes.description: Represents a specific part of a Landing Page, and that section's component type. A Section contains one or more Content blocks (depending on the component) .

contentTypes.name: Link
contentTypes.description: Represents a Link inside a Landing Page Content block.

settings.helpText: Name of the page. Used to generate the slug for the page.
Represents the path to the page, e.g. 'slug-name' creates the page at "https://yourpage.com/slug-name".
Set to true to prevent this page from being indexed by search engines
Used as the page's meta title
Used as the meta description of the page.
Used as the social media image for the page when shared on social media.
The list of sections that will appear on the page
Name of the section. Useful for content editors in Contentful.
Represents the layout of this section.
Represents the heading at the top of the section
Represents the content within the section. Some component types may accept more than one content block.
Name of the Content block. Useful for content editors in Contentful.
Secondary text of context within a section.
Up to two links to be added to the section.
Href field. For internal links, should be relative path (e.g. /path-to-page). For external links, should be an absolute path (e.g. http(s)://my-url.com)
Represents the visible text in the button or link

description.en-US: The Gatsby Landing Page Starter is the fastest way to set up a landing page-based website using Contentful + Gatsby.

heading.en-US: Create custom landing pages using Gatsby and Contentful

primaryText.en-US: This starter-theme combo makes it easy to quickly create custom landing pages in your Gatsby site from Contentful. Use this as a starting point to create custom components that match your visual branding.

secondaryHeading.en-US: Everything you need to start creating landing pages today

primaryText.en-US: The Power of a Theme, with the simplicity of a Starter

secondaryText.en-US: Most of this starter's functionality is built as a Gatsby Theme, meaning you can continue to receive updates and bugfixes after creating your site. Use the starter to quickly suss out a proof-of-concept or start a new project. Use the theme to quickly add landing pages to your existing site.

primaryText.en-US: Content Model Included

secondaryText.en-US: Use the included content model JSON files to scaffold your Contentful Space without having to reinvent the wheel.

primaryText.en-US: Lightweight

secondaryText.en-US: With perfect Lighthouse scores, you can be sure your landing pages are performant, thanks to Gatsby and Gatsby Cloud.

heading.en-US: Get started in minutes & make it your own

primaryText.en-US: Extensible

secondaryText.en-US: The components included in this starter are meant as a starting point to extend the functionality by building your own custom components.

primaryText.en-US: Unopinionated

secondaryText.en-US: This starter uses as few dependencies as possible to create landing pages with Contentful, making it quick and easy to incorporate your own styles to match the look and feel of your brand.

primaryText.en-US: Themeable

secondaryText.en-US: Customize the typography, colors, and components built into this starter to match your own visual branding.

secondaryHeading.en-US: Deploy to Gatsby Cloud or read more in the docs

primaryText.en-US: "Contentful allows content creators at Gatsby to quickly create and edit landing pages without having to coordinate with multiple other teams."
"The landing page theme makes it painless to update styles and add new functionality that our Marketing team can use."
"This is the landing page setup I never knew I wanted until now."
